measurements.description: One fairly flat flower on one 4-cm inflorescence; sepals lanceolate, tips reflexed, lavender-pink, darker medial stripes; petals ovate, lancolate, lavender-pink, darker veins; lip tubular, ruffled edge, white overlaid dark lavender proximally, yellow keel area, keels darker yellow, lavender picotee; column dark lavender, anther cap cream; substance firm; texture crystalline.
